title: Tin Foil Hat #61: QAnon and Black Ops with Tim Dillon
description:
Welcome to another episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli. This episode the boys to Qanon and world of Black Ops with NYC Comic and host of the Tim Dillion is Going To Hell podcast, Tim Dillion. This episode we discuss......
1) Black Ops
2) The Deep State
3) False Flags
4) QAnon
5) Politics is Pro Wrestling
6) Pedogate
Ryan and I would love to thank all of you for helping the podcast have the our best week ever. Without you and your passion we would be anything. Much love to all the Ronins and the Mad Hatters.
